11, "title": "以后的电脑有没有可能干掉内存？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/827298", "created": 1641793944, "deleted": 0, "content": "今天看 CES 发布会，发现 PCIE5.0 的 SSD 读写速度都能上 15GB/s 了\r\n照着这个趋势发展下去，以后会不会出现无需内存的 PC 了", "content_rendered": "<p>今天看 CES 发布会，发现 PCIE5.0 的 SSD 读写速度都能上 15GB/s 了\n照着这个趋势发展下去，以后会不会出现无需内存的 PC 了</p>\n", "last_modified": 1641793944, "replies": 59, "id": 827298}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1635654723", "name": "bb", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1635654723", "title": "宽带症候群", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb", "topics": 10168, "footer": "", "header": "网速很重要。比快更快。", "title_alternative": "Broadband Symptom Complex", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1635654723", "stars": 5307, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 108, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 96357, "username": "Mangle", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Mangle", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/076dc283e5144292641443fcf970efb7?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/076dc283e5144292641443fcf970efb7?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/076dc283e5144292641443fcf970efb7?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1423368908, "last_modified": 1641775515}, "last_reply_by": "gglxh", "last_touched": 1641832275, "title": "2022 求推荐路由器", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/827212", "created": 1641776399, "deleted": 0, "content": "去年下半年接连换了 iphone13pro 和一台支持 wifi6 的电脑，再看看 7,8 年前买的小米路由器，总觉得像小马拉大车。但是近些年除了知道个 wifi6 ，其他路由器的信息都没了解过，希望大佬们能给推荐一个。\r\n\r\n必选项：\r\n1. 预算 500 左右。\r\n2. 支持 wifi6 。\r\n3. 能覆盖 80 平左右的信号强度。这个是核心诉求，屋内的网络结构不太适合组 mesh ，还是希望能一个路由器覆盖整屋。\r\n\r\n可选项：\r\n1. 能刷 openwrt / 支持科学上网。平时想用电视看看 netflix ，能够支持科学上网最好。", "content_rendered": "<p>去年下半年接连换了 iphone13pro 和一台支持 wifi6 的电脑，再看看 7,8 年前买的小米路由器，总觉得像小马拉大车。但是近些年除了知道个 wifi6 ，其他路由器的信息都没了解过，希望大佬们能给推荐一个。</p>\n<p>必选项：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>预算 500 左右。</li>\n<li>支持 wifi6 。</li>\n<li>能覆盖 80 平左右的信号强度。这个是核心诉求，屋内的网络结构不太适合组 mesh ，还是希望能一个路由器覆盖整屋。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>可选项：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>能刷 openwrt / 支持科学上网。平时想用电视看看 netflix ，能够支持科学上网最好。</li>\n</ol>\n", "last_modified": 1641776399, "replies": 56, "id": 827212}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1639060795", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1639060795", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 12531, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1639060795", "stars": 2242, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": "work"}, "member": {"id": 555929, "username": "youshangdepangzi", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/youshangdepangzi", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7822676853df0a8b18ed13361ae4836f?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7822676853df0a8b18ed13361ae4836f?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7822676853df0a8b18ed13361ae4836f?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1631582039, "last_modified": 1640322642}, "last_reply_by": "ffxrqyzby", "last_touched": 1641824466, "title": "不想上班怎么办", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/827233", "created": 1641779794, "deleted": 0, "content": "不想上班，工资挺高，工作不忙，但不想上班，不上班又没钱花，学东西也学不下去，创业也没思虑，但不想上班，怎么搞", "content_rendered": "不想上班，工资挺高，工作不忙，但不想上班，不上班又没钱花，学东西也学不下去，创业也没思虑，但不想上班，怎么搞", "last_modified": 1641779794, "replies": 49, "id": 827233}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df7f/28ac/791_large.png?m=1563424621", "name": "fe", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df7f/28ac/791_normal.png?m=1563424621", "title": "前端开发", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/fe", "topics": 2371, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Frontend", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df7f/28ac/791_mini.png?m=1563424621", "stars": 1126, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 791, "parent_node_name": "programmer"}, "member": {"id": 7928, "username": "wudaown", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/wudaown", "website": "http://wudaown.wordpress.com", "twitter": "wudaown", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9d6b35a889d4ac3c99eeb9e8eae72c2c?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9d6b35a889d4ac3c99eeb9e8eae72c2c?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9d6b35a889d4ac3c99eeb9e8eae72c2c?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1302693322, "last_modified": 1302779988}, "last_reply_by": "crs0910", "last_touched": 1641830734, "title": "React HTTP 请求问题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/827424", "created": 1641820446, "deleted": 0, "content": "各位大佬，\r\n\r\n目前在开发某项目，希望后端不能被外网访问\r\n\r\n前端和外网是通的，可以访问\r\n\r\n前端的机器和后端机器在同一个内网\r\n\r\n现在希望用户访问前端后由前端的机器发起请求而不是从用户网络发起请求。\r\n\r\n\r\n大佬们 这个能做到吗。。\r\n\r\n开发完了 今天测试才想起来网络请求是从用户网络出去的。。这我就很尴尬了。。", "content_rendered": "<p>各位大佬，</p>\n<p>目前在开发某项目，希望后端不能被外网访问</p>\n<p>前端和外网是通的，可以访问</p>\n<p>前端的机器和后端机器在同一个内网</p>\n<p>现在希望用户访问前端后由前端的机器发起请求而不是从用户网络发起请求。</p>\n<p>大佬们 这个能做到吗。。</p>\n<p>开发完了 今天测试才想起来网络请求是从用户网络出去的。。这我就很尴尬了。。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1641820547, "replies": 48, "id": 827424}]